{"tid":1536994,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣覺得 個啲「護士朋友報料」好撚煩","createTime":"2019-09-03T18:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T19:32:41.000Z","uid":13385,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f8d18c5db10e9a833fab2dbdcfc0147011788f53","tid":1536994,"uid":13385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:45:43.000Z","msg":"我知 手足嘅消息 大家都好撚緊張<br />\n<br />\n但呢啲垃圾報料 就慳啲啦 <br />\n<br />\n極度懷疑係啲打手想帶風向 <br />\n<br />\n轉移視射<br />\n<br />\n我深信 手足有咩意外嘅話 醫院/家屬 唔會所有人都同流合污 隱瞞事件<br />\n<br />\n而家 維園喬裝嗰兩個撚屌 拎真槍混入示威者到<br />\n<br />\n係冇撚晒人講咁 <br />\n<br />\n呢兩件都係好撚大嘅事<br />\n<br />\n大家要注意番！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"934922934bb165a8af80af6b999af99b01fbd6b0","tid":1536994,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:45:53.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cf7434f431780431f53c225118ab11940939108","tid":1536994,"uid":13385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:48:31.000Z","msg":"同當時721<br />\n<br />\n個個鄉黑心臟病一撚樣<br />\n又話咩護士報料 醫生報料 醫院報料 <br />\n佢香左 啲𡃁發晒癲 準備亂斬人<br />\n個啲消息一樣<br />\n<br />\n最後點？各位個思路要清晰番啲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8ced655e0cd1baf0fe7f3a4d2204338e624990","tid":1536994,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:49:10.000Z","msg":"快閃既勇武係唔洗代價<br />\n而且少人就成事，大家諗下一個廢老咁慢手腳都可以清晒連儂牆<br />\n對家打埋啲陰陰濕濕既招，我地都可以陰陰濕濕快閃一啲有價值既地方<br />\n十八區都有既時候 啲狗跑得去邊？ 2個人一個地方 36個人都夠<br />\n<br />\n重點：非狗屋 五分鐘快閃"},{"pid":"d9210e2168a3343d0dbc67f2c83369c61bfe92a7","tid":1536994,"uid":317282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:54:49.000Z","msg":"面對着呢啲「報料」<br />\n成日都覺得好雞肋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日睇到啲消息會覺得好嬲又好無助<br />\n有陣時睇得多自然就會諗究竟係真定係假<br />\n呢啲消息往往又好難做fc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到最後都只可以自己同自己講 希望啲消息係假係亂作帶風向<br />\n但係如果係真嘅話 咁就係自己呃緊自己 咁我仲點樣面對呢啲報料消息入邊嘅真正受害者<br />\n信又唔係 唔信又唔係 越諗越覺得煩 越諗越痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔知點樣面對呢啲消息好"},{"pid":"de908fdfb6bf2b4b80b0c30b7a805e3339f05b47","tid":1536994,"uid":13385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9210e2168a3343d0dbc67f2c83369c61bfe92a7","tid":1536994,"uid":317282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:54:49.000Z","msg":"面對着呢啲「報料」<br />\n成日都覺得好雞肋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日睇到啲消息會覺得好嬲又好無助<br />\n有陣時睇得多自然就會諗究竟係真定係假<br />\n呢啲消息往往又好難做fc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到最後都只可以自己同自己講 希望啲消息係假係亂作帶風向<br />\n但係如果係真嘅話 咁就係自己呃緊自己 咁我仲點樣面對呢啲報料消息入邊嘅真正受害者<br />\n信又唔係 唔信又唔係 越諗越覺得煩 越諗越痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔知點樣面對呢啲消息好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:58:35.000Z","msg":"加句fact checked 就係fact check左<br />\n<br />\n朋友報料 都是假的 fact checked"},{"pid":"7e453ce8c8f2f0883368bd2efa79188945e51a10","tid":1536994,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:12:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iBWrQR5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiBWrQR5.jpg&h=8316617f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d781e9b60bff95df936b0ccd28bfab4b62a3981","tid":1536994,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ktasvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ktasvY.jpg&h=e8e5ebbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwTmzaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwTmzaZ.jpg&h=1a577aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yz5kaNx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYz5kaNx.jpg&h=f4f7f731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機場壓力測試，其實係連「機場」都唔需要入的<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531743</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"21090dd4450257f488f0fb92c511cf231d74704a","tid":1536994,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201